<paper id="1584180009"><title>On the performance of hyperelliptic cryptosystems</title><year>1999</year><authors><author org="Hewlett Packard Labs., Bristol, UK" id="2110748698">Nigel P. Smart</author></authors><n_citation>41</n_citation><doc_type>Conference</doc_type><references><reference>1492538628</reference><reference>1496801598</reference><reference>1507106163</reference><reference>1535853723</reference><reference>1551624585</reference><reference>1560603711</reference><reference>1571136570</reference><reference>1938064843</reference><reference>1979485530</reference><reference>1989258293</reference><reference>2046569422</reference><reference>2069512128</reference><reference>2077958919</reference><reference>2091826091</reference><reference>2091987928</reference><reference>2111310412</reference><reference>2912690715</reference></references><venue id="1140213147" type="C">Theory and Application of Cryptographic Techniques</venue><doi>10.1007/3-540-48910-X_12</doi><keywords><keyword weight="0.42166">Discrete mathematics</keyword><keyword weight="0.7189">Hyperelliptic curve</keyword><keyword weight="0.62777">Supersingular elliptic curve</keyword><keyword weight="0.40452">Computer science</keyword><keyword weight="0.48181">Cryptography</keyword><keyword weight="0.70973">Hyperelliptic curve cryptography</keyword><keyword weight="0.57895">Jacobian curve</keyword><keyword weight="0.49787">Elliptic curve</keyword><keyword weight="0.61343">Counting points on elliptic curves</keyword><keyword weight="0.49693">Discrete logarithm</keyword></keywords><publisher>Springer, Berlin, Heidelberg</publisher><abstract>In this paper we discuss various aspects of cryptosystems based on hyperelliptic curves. In particular we cover the implementation of the group law on such curves and how to generate suitable curves for use in cryptography. This paper presents a practical comparison between the performance of elliptic curve based digital signature schemes and schemes based on hyperelliptic curves. We conclude that, at present, hyperelliptic curves offer no performance advantage over elliptic curves.</abstract></paper>